NBA WESTERN CONFERENCE FINALS: SUNS v LAKERS
May 21, 2010
Lamar Odom
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







 Q. In your strive for perfection, which you never can reach, what is it that you're working on now? 
 LAMAR ODOM: Me? 

 Q. Yes. 
 LAMAR ODOM: Just defend. Defend. Defend. 

 Q. Never play defense well enough?
 LAMAR ODOM: Win defense. That's how you win games. 
 Of course, that's how you win championships. 







END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT